title: 3 BED 2 BATH! WON'T LAST LONG! APPLY TODAY!
posting_body: ['Call Us Today', 'show contact info', 'This ground floor corner Three Bedroom Two Bathroom apartment home with wood flooring throughout comes with a spacious, extra large RENOVATED kitchen with a pantry and plentiful cabinet and counter space, all Brand new!', 'Living and dining rooms are set up perfect for entertaining!', "When you live at La Terrazza, you're in good hands with our professionally trained leasing and maintenance staff.", 'We welcome you and want you to live remarkably during your stay with us whether it is short or long-term.', "Enjoy our many amenities including: our new state-of-art fitness center, basketball courts, children's play area, computer room, and private entry to the Colma BART station!", 'All of our homes come with full size washer/dryers, heat and air conditioning, generous closet space, double-pane windows, two-tone paint and beautiful wood-like flooring in the kitchen, dining and bathrooms.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday: Closed', 'Tuesday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Wednesday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Thursday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Friday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 09:00 AM - 05:00 PM', 'Sunday: Closed', 'La Terrazza Apartments', '7800 El Camino Real', 'More Photos', '<URL>']
